    • Constructor Detail

      • Preprocessor

        @SafeVarargs
public Preprocessor(BiFunction<Request,Model,? extends Collection<Statement>>... filters)
        Creates an RDF preprocessor.

        Filters are chained in the specified order and executed on incoming requests and their RDF payload, if one is present, or ignored, otherwise.

        Parameters:
        filters - the request RDF preprocessing filters to be inserted; ech filter takes as argument an incoming request and its RDF payload and must return a non-null RDF model
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if filters is null or contains null values
